subject: Hello Sir,
body:
Hello Sir,
I want to reveal to you all that has been happening here at CBN over
your fund for years, get back to me for detailed information.
Jane Oparah

subject: Re:  Hello Sir,
body:
Hello Jane Oparah,

Thank you for reaching out to me. I'm curious to know more about what has been happening with my fund at CBN. Could you please provide me with some detailed information? I appreciate your willingness to share this with me.

Looking forward to hearing from you soon.

Best wishes,
David

subject: Re: Hello Sir,
body:
Hello David,

I tried as much to explain all I know about your fund at CBN by letting
know what has been happening. What you need now is to contact the lawyer in
charge of the process.

Let me hear from you to give you the contact details of the lawyer.
Thanks,

Ms. Jane Oparah.
